The anticipated AMVCA was a night to remember for awardees, viewers and fans. Stars dazzled in their intricate African fabric but somewhat western styled designs. Some designs were outright jaw-dropping and some elicited traction for days. Some stars went all out to wow with their lacy inspirations and thigh-high slit dresses. Some conservative people have termed the slit dresses above board and unafrican. Here are some stars that graced the red carpet with the slits. Sharon Ooja Inidima Okojie Sika Osei Meg Otanwa What do you think?